<mvc:View 
 xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt" 
 xmlns:uxap="sap.uxap" 
 controllerName="project1.controller.ProductDetails"
 xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
 xmlns="sap.m">
    <uxap:ObjectPageLayout id="idObjectPageLayout">
        <uxap:headerTitle>
            <uxap:ObjectPageDynamicHeaderTitle >
                <uxap:expandedHeading>
                    <Title text="Product Title"></Title>
                </uxap:expandedHeading>

                <uxap:snappedHeading>
                    <Title text="Product Title"/>
                </uxap:snappedHeading>

                <uxap:expandedContent>
                    <Text text="product description"/>
                </uxap:expandedContent>

                <uxap:snappedContent>
                    <Text text="product description"/>
                </uxap:snappedContent>               
            </uxap:ObjectPageDynamicHeaderTitle>
        </uxap:headerTitle>

        <uxap:headerContent>
            <VBox>
                <Title text="release information"></Title>
                <ObjectStatus title="Total time" text="XX days"></ObjectStatus>
                <ObjectStatus state="Success" text="SALE" class="sapMObjectStatusLarge"></ObjectStatus>
                <tnt:InfoLabel text="New"></tnt:InfoLabel>
            </VBox>
        </uxap:headerContent>

        <uxap:sections>
            <uxap:ObjectPageSection id="idProductDetailSection" title="Product Details">
                <uxap:subSections>
                    <uxap:ObjectPageSubSection >
                        <uxap:blocks>
                            <mvc:XMLView viewName="project1.view.sections.ProductDetailsSection"></mvc:XMLView>
                        </uxap:blocks>
                    </uxap:ObjectPageSubSection>
                </uxap:subSections>
            </uxap:ObjectPageSection>
            
            <uxap:ObjectPageSection id="idProductSuppliersSection" title="Suppliers">
                <uxap:subSections>
                    <uxap:ObjectPageSubSection >
                         <uxap:blocks>
                            <mvc:XMLView viewName="project1.view.sections.SuppliersSection"></mvc:XMLView>
                        </uxap:blocks>
                    </uxap:ObjectPageSubSection>
                </uxap:subSections>
            </uxap:ObjectPageSection>

            <uxap:ObjectPageSection id="idProductCommentsSection" title="Comments">
                <uxap:subSections>
                    <uxap:ObjectPageSubSection >
                         <uxap:blocks>
                            <mvc:XMLView viewName="project1.view.sections.CommentsSection"></mvc:XMLView>
                        </uxap:blocks>
                    </uxap:ObjectPageSubSection>
                </uxap:subSections>
            </uxap:ObjectPageSection>
        </uxap:sections>
    </uxap:ObjectPageLayout>
</mvc:View>